# LucaB: "If you're thinking of starting a bootstrapped DeFi curation business: don't"

**Source:** [@LucaB_Cassa thread](https://x.com/LucaB_Cassa/status/2041410696378982483) — April 7, 2026
**Stats:** 46 likes, 11.7K views

